    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/28b30c42e566b24fb991c387f7cc1eb4.poster.avif?t=1753795755\" width=800 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/28b30c42e566b24fb991c387f7cc1eb4.webm?t=1753795755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“音乐是我们的过去和未来。” 探索一个以音乐为灵感的丰富塔防抽卡 RPG！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/cc4e2a69694c7fae8c2226f5cf0f8596.avif?t=1753795755\" width=616 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/4011a292098c8d710c15f3ecebcf9eb2.poster.avif?t=1753795755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/4011a292098c8d710c15f3ecebcf9eb2.webm?t=1753795755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/4011a292098c8d710c15f3ecebcf9eb2.mp4?t=1753795755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♪ 独特且可爱的角色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    每个角色都基于不同的乐器和音乐流派设计得十分精美。享受他们在技能动画中的高清插画，以及战场上的可爱Q版形象。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/848a81a810ed16824d1f8570f2c8945c.avif?t=1753795755\" width=616 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/1e9c9c4f242020519b65974be91d44b7.poster.avif?t=1753795755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/1e9c9c4f242020519b65974be91d44b7.webm?t=1753795755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/1e9c9c4f242020519b65974be91d44b7.mp4?t=1753795755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♪ 策略性和深度并存的玩法</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    游戏发布时提供10种音乐流派和7种音乐师角色类型。培养并打造属于您的音乐师阵容，掌握激烈的实时战斗游戏玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/e256835b040b24acd961c2a933862f6c.avif?t=1753795755\" width=616 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/06ac88ce78861d84ca1497cd2a09029b.poster.avif?t=1753795755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/06ac88ce78861d84ca1497cd2a09029b.webm?t=1753795755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/06ac88ce78861d84ca1497cd2a09029b.mp4?t=1753795755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♪ 兴奋的塔防</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在惊心动魄的塔防战斗中，部署维塔士抵御一波又一波的敌人，考验你的策略。结合音乐能力和独特原型，克服复杂挑战，保持节奏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/e16b347f1d049903acc60785f724b90e.avif?t=1753795755\" width=616 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/c07a3186e8557a519f9b54cbf5d969fc.poster.avif?t=1753795755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/c07a3186e8557a519f9b54cbf5d969fc.webm?t=1753795755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/c07a3186e8557a519f9b54cbf5d969fc.mp4?t=1753795755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♪ 复杂的世界构建</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    进入一个隐藏着许多秘密的详细世界，体验充满曲折的视觉小说风格的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/d3fcda9beb9040a2f93e4c2e66a39461.avif?t=1753795755\" width=616 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/b7e2e3da856e8b1c8e21d7d4ce9a5b47.poster.avif?t=1753795755\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/b7e2e3da856e8b1c8e21d7d4ce9a5b47.webm?t=1753795755\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/b7e2e3da856e8b1c8e21d7d4ce9a5b47.mp4?t=1753795755\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♪ 高品质的背景音乐 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    一个以音乐为基础的世界，通过音乐来表达。聆听根据您的游戏玩法变化的音轨！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180780/extras/28b30c42e566b24fb991c387f7cc1eb